  "text": "The construction of FLI1-expressing and PDEF-expressing adenovirus has been previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Cells were infected in normal growth medium using the lowest dilution of either control virus expressing green fluorescent protein (Ad-GFP) or virus expressing FLI1/GFP (Ad-FLI1) or PDEF/GFP (Ad-PDEF) that yielded N 95% infected MDA-MB-231 cells assessed by GFP expression. Infected cells were then incubated as normal for 16 to 20 hours.",
